<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='69310' id='t-69310'>let me play 20 seconds
from a story that we used,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='73318' id='t-73318'>told by a very talented storyteller,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='75666' id='t-75666'>Jim O'Grady.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='78244' id='t-78244'>(Audio) Jim O'Grady: So I'm banging out
