<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='163810' id='t-163810'>and then I start to make it --</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='165362' id='t-165362'>UH: Suddenly, you can see
