<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='217125' id='t-217125'>Now these two cylinders start to rotate.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='219761' id='t-219761'>This rotation vibration
is going through the wood</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='222914' id='t-222914'>and is going to couple
