</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='227579' id='t-227579'>(Synchronized clicking)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:08
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='237834' id='t-237834'>This is what you call
