<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='240482' id='t-240482'>Now let's go back to the brain and ask:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='242749' id='t-242749'>What's driving this neural entrainment?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244917' id='t-244917'>Is it simply the sounds
