</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288051' id='t-288051'>Now we can take these sounds
